name: Wire Tree
description: Every tree is different and hand made. Some have brown leaves, some have crystal/white, and some have black. In the Picture is a medium sized tree. They will come attached to a shell or stone unless you select the option of the glass jar ecosystem. The ecosystem has synthetic moss lining the bottom with the tree nestled on top. The tree size will automatically be medium if this option is selected.
